728437f-a.title: Richmond: Arthur Kill Road - Miles Avenue
728437f-a.text:
Arthur Kill Road, north side, at Miles Avenue.
This house belonged to Daniel H. Hanckel (1917) and earlier
to Adelaide E. Bellows (1907 and 1898). Ie, 1874 it belonged
to H. S. Samuels. The dates refer to maps cpon which the
onwers' names appear.
February 17, 1929
P. L. Sperr
NO REFRODUCTIONS
